                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Following the success of the New York Times bestseller How to Marry the Man of Your Choice, The Rules is a blunt, effective, controversial, funny, and definitive guide to marrying the man of your dreams. The Rules will be featured on an Oprah show, set to air close to Valentine's Day.</span>
              
